IMAGES

The "crate-texture.jpg" image is taken from
Gabriel Gambetta's GitHub repository (https://github.com/ggambetta/computer-graphics-from-scratch)
and he has released it under the "Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0
International license" (BY-NC-SA) which can be found at:
https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

The "crate-texture-mipmap.jpg" image is derived from Gabriel's "crate-texture.jpg" image and is
released under the same license.

The "crate-texture-mipmap-checkerboard.jpg" and "crate-texture-mipmap-false-color.jpg" images are
my original images and not based on Gabriel's work. They are released under the same license for
consistency.

The "medieval_wood_diff_1k.jpg" texture and associated "medieval_wood_nor_gl_1k.jpg" normal map are
from the https://polyhaven.com/ website and are released under a Creative Commons "CC0 1.0"
license, which can be found at:
https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/
